Makes: 6 sandwiches Cheesy Peppadew corn bread: 250ml (1 cup) corn kernels, fresh or frozen 4 Peppadews, finely chopped 3 eggs, lightly beaten 250ml (1 cup) buttermilk 60ml (¼ cup) vegetable oil 5ml (1 tsp) dried chilli flakes 120g (1 cup) cake flour 60g (½ cup) maize meal 15ml (1 tbsp) baking powder 5ml (1 tsp) sugar Pinch of salt 100g (1 cup) grated cheddar cheese To serve: 1 avocado, peeled and mashed Juice of 1 small lemon A handful roasted pistachio nuts 2 radishes, sliced A handful of pea shoots Method: